snippet.title: Hearts of Iron IV: Götterdämmerung | Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Hearts of Iron IV: Götterdämmerung - Buy now! https://pdxint.at/EP1Store

Explore new alternate histories and geopolitical options for the key player in World War II, the German Reich. A larger German national focus tree takes center stage in this expansion, alongside smaller trees for Austria, Hungary and Belgium, as well as new scientific and military options.

#hoi4 #heartsofironiv #götterdammerung
